  "merge_notes": "Both cards are ICT school; no conflict. The first card emphasizes daily profile context (Seek and Destroy, London Reversal, New York Reversal) and includes 10:00 EST level; the second card adds AMD cycle framing, standard deviation projections, and more detailed entry rules (CISD on lower timeframe, SMT divergence). Unified card preserves both perspectives.",
